#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/67/
msgid "Murlocs - APM"
msgstr "鱼人 - 手速倒转"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/67/
msgid "First, have a ton of economy, typically starting from golden [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] or Brann + [[Magicfin Mycologist||122277]], remembering premium economy spells such as Cloning Conch or Battlecry Discovery. Then, your payoff card for all that economy is typically [[Primitive Painter||122281]]. Your payoff can also include [[Bream Counter||98509]] + [[Mrglin'Burglar||114391]] handbuff package, or [[Cousin Errgl||131149]] family package. In any case, you're scaling [[Expert Aviator||126637]], which is the most premium murloc because it can summon any scam card ([[Leeroy The Reckless||90425]]) from your hand."
msgstr "首先，要有大量的经济，通常要从有金色[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] 或铜须+ [[Magicfin Mycologist||122277]]开始，让小学生记住高级经济法术，如克隆螺号或发现战吼。然后，所有这些经济的回报卡通常是[[Primitive Painter||122281]]。你的回报也可以包括 [[Bream Counter||98509]] + [[Mrglin'Burglar||114391]] 手牌强化组合，或 [[Cousin Errgl||131149]] 家族组合。无论如何，你都在提升 [[Expert Aviator||126637]]，这是最好的鱼人，因为它可以从手牌召唤任何下毒卡 ([[Leeroy The Reckless||90425]]) 。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/67/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + lots of economy + Murloc scaling ([[Primitive Painter||122281]])"
msgstr "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + 大量经济 + 鱼人强化 ([[Primitive Painter||122281]])"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/67/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"
msgstr "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/67/
msgid "Cycle cards to scale murlocs"
msgstr "循环刷牌来强化鱼人"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "Undead - Attack Scaling"
msgstr "亡灵 - 攻击提升"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "Scale the attack of your Undeads and summons with the Butchering spell from [[Drustfallen Butcher||120104]]. Butchering doubles it's effect when paired with [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]], and also improves with spell scaling from [[Friendly Geist||120219]] or [[Tranquil Meditative||119942]]. Your quality of summons come from [[Handless Forsaken||95265]], but also could use [[Deathly Striker||115610]] or [[Eternal Summoner||95263]]. Be sure to reborn as many key undeads as possible, starting with [[Handless Forsaken||95265]]. Using [[Disguised Graverobber||104610]] on [[Mummifier||108992]] also gives permanent reborns."
msgstr "使用来自 [[Drustfallen Butcher||120104]] 的宰割法术来提升你的亡灵和召唤物的攻击力。宰割法术在与 [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]] 搭配时效果翻倍，并且也能从 [[Friendly Geist||120219]] 或 [[Tranquil Meditative||119942]] 的法术加成中获益。你的召唤物的品质来自 [[Handless Forsaken||95265]]，但也可以使用 [[Deathly Striker||115610]] 或 [[Eternal Summoner||95263]]。确保尽可能多地复生关键亡灵，从 [[Handless Forsaken||95265]] 开始贴复生。在 [[Mummifier||108992]] 上使用 [[Disguised Graverobber||104610]] 也能提供永久复生。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "Attack Scaling ([[Drustfallen Butcher||120104]]) + summons ([[Handless Forsaken||95265]])"
msgstr "攻击成长 ([[Drustfallen Butcher||120104]]) + 亡灵召唤([[Handless Forsaken||95265]])"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "[[Deathly Striker||115610]] \n"
"[[Friendly Geist||120219]]"
msgstr "[[Deathly Striker||115610]] \n"
"[[Friendly Geist||120219]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/14/
msgid "Summon high attack Undeads"
msgstr "召唤高攻击力的亡灵"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/32/
msgid "Mechs - Automaton (SPECIFIC HEROES)"
msgstr "机械 - 星元自动机（特定英雄）"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/32/
msgid "Reborn your Automaton as soon as possible to start scaling it. Put naked [[Auto Assembler||120025]] on the board to also scale it. Roll on 5 for Kangors, and then you can fill out the rest of your comp with Leeroy and scam."
msgstr "尽快复生你的自动机以开始强化它。将单独的[[Auto Assembler||120025]] 放在棋盘上来强化它。在5级酒馆刷新找坎格尔的学徒，然后你可以用火车王和其他下毒卡来完成你的流派。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/32/
msgid "Automaton + Enabled Hero/Trinket"
msgstr "星元自动机 + 特定英雄/饰品"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/32/
msgid "Lich King, Akazamarak (Pack Tactics), and Teron Gorefield"
msgstr "巫妖王，阿卡扎曼扎拉克（集群战术），塔隆·血魔"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/32/
msgid "Summon large Automatons"
msgstr "召唤大型星元自动机"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/82/
msgid "Back to Back"
msgstr "背靠背"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/82/
msgid "Scale spell power with [[Felfire Conjurer||120299]] + [[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]] to make your Back to Back (Tavern Spell) bigger. Then, use [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]] to double the scaling and effectiveness of your back to backs. [[Cataclysmic Harbinger||130884]] allows you to print multiple of them every turn. Scale premium units such as [[Sinrunner Blanchy]]."
msgstr "使用 [[Felfire Conjurer||120299]] + [[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]] 来提升法术强度，使你的背靠背（酒馆法术）变得更大。然后使用 [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]] 将其数值和效果翻倍。[[Cataclysmic Harbinger||130884]] 能让你每回合印多个背靠背。提升高级单位，如 [[罪奔者布兰契]]。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/82/
msgid "Back to Back generation ([[Cataclysmic Harbinger||130884]]) + spell power ([[Felfire Conjurer||120299]]) + [[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]]"
msgstr "背靠背生成 ([[Cataclysmic Harbinger||130884]]) + 法术强化 ([[Felfire Conjurer||120299]]) + [[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]]"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/82/
msgid "[[Cataclysmic Harbinger||130884]]\n"
"[[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]]"
msgstr "[[Cataclysmic Harbinger||130884]]\n"
"[[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/82/
msgid "Scale and repeatedly play specific tavern spell"
msgstr "成长并重复施放特定酒馆法术"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/15/
msgid "Dragons - Battlecries"
msgstr "龙 - 战吼"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/15/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + [[Kalecgos, Arcane Aspect||60630]] gives all of your dragons +4/4 every single battlecry you play. You want to trigger as many battlecries as possible. After you have your setup, cycle only PREMIUM battlecries, such as [[Tavern Tempest||64077]], [[Refreshing Anomaly||64042]], [[Shell Collector||80740]] or [[Draconic Warden||126860]]. You may run [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Draconic Warden||126860]], which farms a lot of battlecries and triples which help a lot with board strength and economy."
msgstr "每当你施放一个战吼，[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + [[Kalecgos, Arcane Aspect||60630]] 会使你所有龙获得+4/4。你需要尽可能多地触发战吼。当你完成阵容搭建后，只使用高级战吼，例如[[Tavern Tempest||64077]], [[Refreshing Anomaly||64042]],  [[Shell Collector||80740]] 或 [[Draconic Warden||126860]]。你可以使用 [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Draconic Warden||126860]]，这能产生大量战吼和三连，对场面和经济都非常有帮助。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/15/
msgid "[[Kalecgos, Arcane Aspect||60630]] + [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"
msgstr "[[Kalecgos, Arcane Aspect||60630]] + [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/15/
msgid "Cycle battlecries to scale dragons"
msgstr "循环使用战吼来强化龙的属性"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid "Pirates - Bounty APM"
msgstr "海盗 - 悬赏令手速倒转"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid "[[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]] combined with [[Proud Privateer||122520]] gives you lots of gold to hit more of your setup.  Cycle [[Tranquil Meditative||119942]], or spell buff Chromadrakes with Brann for spell scaling to make your bounties buff more. You also want to cycle every single free card ([[Refreshing Anomaly||64042]]) and [[Roving Sailor||130705]] so you stay infinite. You may want to scale using [[Brazen Buccaneer||130703]] + [[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]] as well. ADVANCED PLAYERS: After you're infinite, think about the highest possible scaling from your spot. Options include Shop Buff Demons Pivot or [[Fire-forged Evoker||120301]] Pivot or Attack Scaling Undead pivot ([[Forsaken Weaver||126733]])"
msgstr "[[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]] 与 [[Proud Privateer||122520]] 组合，能为你提供大量铸币，让你能构建更多卡牌。循环 [[Tranquil Meditative||119942]],，或者用铜须给多彩幼龙加法术强度，让你的悬赏令卡获得更多增益。你还需要循环每一张免费卡牌 ([[Refreshing Anomaly||64042]]) 和 [[Roving Sailor||130705]]，这样你就能保持无限资源。你也可以考虑使用 [[Brazen Buccaneer||130703]] + [[Drakkari Enchanter||101314]] 来提升强度。进阶玩家：当你达到无限资源后，要考虑从你的卡组中获得最高的强度。选项包括转成商店增益恶魔流派或 [[Fire-forged Evoker||120301]流派，或者攻击强化亡灵流([[Forsaken Weaver||126733]])"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid "Bounty Generation ([[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]]) + [[Proud Privateer||122520]]"
msgstr "悬赏令生成器 ([[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]]) + [[Proud Privateer||122520]]"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid "Midgame Bounties ([[Bigwig Bandit||122179]]/[[Lost City Looter||122175]])"
msgstr "中期获取悬赏令 ([[Bigwig Bandit||122179]]/[[Lost City Looter||122175]])"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/3/
msgid "Bounties generate gold and stats"
msgstr "靠悬赏令生成铸币和身材数值"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/84/
msgid "Quilboar - Combat Scaling"
msgstr "野猪人 - 战斗提升"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/84/
msgid "Scale your gems mainly using [[Prickly Piper||98946]] and [[Dreaming Thornweaver||120708]] and cycling every [[Moon-Bacon Jazzer||98930]] and [[Fearless Foodie||113154]] that you see. Then, Using [[Redtusk Thornraiser||130153]] to reborn all your quilboars, most importantly Piper and [[Three Lil Quilboar||114486]]. [[Bristlebach||100997]] makes you really strong because of all your reborns, especially when paired with reborn [[Glowgullet Warlord||120031]]. You may reborn taunt [[Pufferquil||97549]], so the reborned Pufferquil also gets venom. You may run an [[Earthsong Shaman||130149]] just to add many stats at the end of the turn. Of course, cycle every [[Hog Watcher||122737]] to give your quilboars Divine Shield."
msgstr "主要使用 [[Prickly Piper||98946]] 和 [[Dreaming Thornweaver||120708]] 来提升你的宝石，并且循环使用你遇到的每一个 [[Moon-Bacon Jazzer||98930]] 和 [[Fearless Foodie||113154]]。然后，使用 [[Redtusk Thornraiser||130153]] 来复生所有的你的野猪人，最重要的是刺头吹笛人和 [[Three Lil Quilboar||114486]]。 [[Bristlebach||100997]] 让你变得非常强大，因为你所有的随从都有复生，尤其是在与复生的 [[Glowgullet Warlord||120031]] 组合时。你可以复生嘲讽的 [[Pufferquil||97549]]，这样复活后的刺豚野猪也会获得烈毒。你可以留一个 [[Earthsong Shaman||130149]]，只是为了在回合结束时增加很多属性。当然，循环使用每一个 [[Hog Watcher||122737]]，给你的野猪人加圣盾。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/84/
msgid "Gem scaling ([[Prickly Piper||98946]]) + Combat scaling ([[Bristlebach||100997]])"
msgstr "宝石强化([Prickly Piper||98946]]) + 战斗中强化([[Bristlebach||100997]])"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/84/
msgid "Gem scaling ([[Prickly Piper||98946]])"
msgstr "宝石强化 ([[Prickly Piper||98946]])"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/84/
msgid "Unleash high attack gems during combat."
msgstr "战斗中施放高攻击宝石。"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/85/
msgid "Nagas - Combat Scaling/Spell Buff"
msgstr "纳迦 - 战斗成长/法术强化"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/85/
msgid "Proc [[Ruthless Queensguard||126918]]'s deathratte effect as many times as possible. Your Queen's commands benefit from spell buff ([[Tranquil Meditative||119942]]). [[Maelstrom Emergent||126633]], [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]], reborn on it, [[Titus Rivendare||97408]], [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]], [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] all add multiplier effects on the amount of Queen's Command you cast."
msgstr "尽可能多次触发[[Ruthless Queensguard||126918]]的亡语效果。你的女王的命令因法强([[Tranquil Meditative||119942]])而受益。[[Maelstrom Emergent||126633]], [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] 给他们复生，[[Titus Rivendare||97408]], [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]], [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] 都会为你的女王的命令施放增加倍率效果。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/85/
msgid "[[Ruthless Queensguard||126918]] + Spell Scaling ([[Tranquil Meditative||119942]])"
msgstr "[[Ruthless Queensguard||126918]] + 法术强化 ([[Tranquil Meditative||119942]])"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/85/
msgid "[[Ruthless Queensguard||126918]]\n"
"Spell scaling ([[Tranquil Meditative||119942]])"
msgstr "[[Ruthless Queensguard||126918]]\n"
"法术强化 ([[Tranquil Meditative||119942]])"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/85/
msgid "Scale nagas in combat"
msgstr "在战斗中强化纳迦"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "Demons - Damage"
msgstr "恶魔 - 伤害"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "[[Lord of the Ruins||122116]] buffs by having your demons deal damage to minions. The best way to do that is with [[Silent Enforcer||122605]] + [[Titus Rivendare||97408]], which damages all your opponent's minions at once. [[Devout Hellcaller||122586]] and [[Tarecgosa||72062]] are ways to get permanent scaling."
msgstr "[[Lord of the Ruins||122116]] 通过让你的恶魔对随从造成伤害来获得属性。最好的方法是使用 [[Silent Enforcer||122605]] + [[Titus Rivendare||97408]]，它能一次性对对手所有随从造成伤害。[[Devout Hellcaller||122586]] 和 [[Tarecgosa||72062]] 是获得永久成长的方式。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "[[Silent Enforcer||122605]] + Damage payoff ([[Lord of the Ruins||122116]])"
msgstr "[[Silent Enforcer||122605]] + 受伤回报 ([[Lord of the Ruins||122116]])"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "[[Lord of the Ruins||122116]]"
msgstr "[[Lord of the Ruins||122116]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/51/
msgid "Demons deal damage to buff board"
msgstr "恶魔造成伤害来增强棋盘"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/59/
msgid "Quilboar - Darkgaze"
msgstr "野猪人 - 暗视"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/59/
msgid "After you have [[Darkgaze Elder||80756]] and buffed gems ([[Prickly Piper||98946]]), your objective is to spend as much gold as possible. This is usually done if you have [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]], and you cycle every free battlecry such as [[Shell Collector||80740]] and [[Tavern Tempest||64077]]. You also want to cycle every [[Moon bacon Jazzer||98930]] and [[Fearless foodie||113154]] to help scale. Any quilboar in the addon section is good to fill out the rest of your board."
msgstr "在获得 [[Darkgaze Elder||80756]] 和强化宝石([[Prickly Piper||98946]])后，你的目标是尽可能多地花费铸币。通常情况下如果你拥有[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]，你会循环使用所有免费的战吼，例如 [[Shell Collector||80740]] 和 [[Tavern Tempest||64077]]。你还需要循环使用所有 [[Moon bacon Jazzer||98930]] 和 [[Fearless foodie||113154]] 来提升宝石属性。在附加卡牌栏中的任何野猪人都是适合用来填补剩余棋盘空位的。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/59/
msgid "[[Darkgaze Elder||80756]] + Scaled gems ([[Prickly Piper||98946]])"
msgstr "[[Darkgaze Elder||80756]] + 宝石强化 ([[Prickly Piper||98946]])"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/59/
msgid "Spend gold to cast blood gems"
msgstr "花费铸币施放鲜血宝石"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "Mechs - Deathrattle"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "First, have a deathrattle midgame to have a scaled [[Falling Sky Golem||130798]] already. Taunt reborn it. Resummon it with [[Kangor's apprentice||59935]]. Fill out the rest of your board with scam such as [[Leeroy the Reckless||90425]]."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "[[Falling Sky Golem||130798]] + [[Kangor's Apprentice||59935]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "Big [[Falling Sky Golem||130798]]"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/68/
msgid "Summon huge golems"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "Nagas - Deep Blue"
msgstr "纳迦 - 深沉蓝调"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "Roll for [[Deep Blue Crooner||98886]], [[Zesty Shaker||99054]], and [[Flaming Enforcer||126924]]. Put your spellcrafts on the shop with Enforcer to gain permanent stats. [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]] doubles your deepblue stats and scaling if you use it on your board. After you have golden versions of everything, start filling out the rest of your board with scam such as [[Leeroy the Reckless||90425]]."
msgstr "刷新酒馆只拿 [[Deep Blue Crooner||98886]], [[Zesty Shaker||99054]] 和 [[Flaming Enforcer||126924]]。将你的塑造法术施加在魔焰执行者上，以获得永久属性加成。 [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]] 能让你的深沉蓝调属性翻倍。当你拥有所有金色版本后，用烈毒填充你棋盘的其余部分，例如 [[Leeroy the Reckless||90425]]。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "Early [[Deep Blue Crooner||98886]] + [[Zesty Shaker||99054]]"
msgstr "早期获得 [[Deep Blue Crooner||98886]] + [[Zyury Shaker||99054]]"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "[[Deep Blue Crooner||98886]]\n"
"[[Zesty Shaker||99054]]"
msgstr "[[Deep Blue Crooner||98886]]\n"
"[[Zesty Shaker||99054]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/58/
msgid "Scale Naga's spellcraft"
msgstr "强化纳迦的塑造法术"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "Mechs - Divine Shield"
msgstr "机械 - 圣盾"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "Use [[Charging Czarina||110321]] to buff your divine shields. [[Deflect-o-bot||61930]] is your best divine shield unit, while [[Divine Sparkbot||123644]] + reborn is your spell generation. Buy every spell that effectively costs 1 (such as [[Recruit a Trainee||103793]] and [[Fortify||103791]])."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "2x [[Charging Czarina||110321]] or [[Charging Czarina||110321]] + [[Divine Sparkbot||123644]]"
msgstr "2x [[Charging Czarina||110321]] 或 [[Charging Czarina||110321]] + [[Divine Sparkbot||123644]]"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "Divine Shields ([[Deflect-o-bot||61930]])"
msgstr "圣盾([[Deflect-o-bot||61930]])"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/21/
msgid "Play spells to buff Mechs"
msgstr "释放酒馆法术来增强机械"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/20/
msgid "Nagas - Groundbreaker"
msgstr "纳迦 - 碎地者"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/20/
msgid "First, you must have had a Naga midgame so you casted a lot of spells. Your naga generation setup consists of [[Seafloor Recruiter||126916]] + [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]] and/or [[Maelstrom Emergent||126633]]. After you have at least 2 Groundbreakers, cycle every naga that has a good effect on top of it, such as [[Shell collector||80740]] and [[Darkcrest Strategist||115555]]."
msgstr "首先，你必须拥有过中期过度纳迦，因此你施放过大量的法术。你的纳迦生成阵容由 [[Seafloor Recruiter||126916]] + [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]] 和/或 [[Maelstrom Emergent||126633]] 组成。在你至少拥有2个碎地者后，循环使用那些对它有良好效果的纳迦，例如 [[Shell collector||80740]] 和 [[Darkcrest Strategist||115555]]。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/20/
msgid "[[Seafloor Recruiter||126916]] plus [[Groundbreaker||114816]]"
msgstr "[[Seafloor Recruiter||126916]] + [[Groundbreaker||114816]]"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/20/
msgid "[[Seafloor Recruiter||126916]]"
msgstr "[[Seafloor Recruiter||126916]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/20/
msgid "Play spells and nagas to scale"
msgstr "打出法术和纳迦来成长"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/83/
msgid "Beasts - Leviathan"
msgstr "野兽 - 深潜巨兽"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/83/
msgid "Summon as many beasts as possible after you get early [[Lurking Leviathan||130711]]. You either use [[Sewer Lord||130996]] and/or [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]]. Then, paired with [[Banana Slamma||98824]], every summon will have a ton of attack. Reborn on [[Sewer Lord||130996]] provides so many summons."
msgstr "在你早期获得 [[Lurking Leviathan||130711]] 后，尽可能多地召唤野兽。你可以使用 [[Sewer Lord||130996]] 和/或 [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]]。然后，与 [[Banana Slamma||98824]] 搭配，每个召唤物都会拥有大量的攻击力。给 [[Sewer Lord||130996]] 复生会提供大量的召唤物。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/83/
msgid "Early [[Lurking Leviathan||130711]] + Beast summons ([[Sewer Lord||130996]])"
msgstr "早期获得[[Lurking Leviathan||130711]] + 野兽召唤([[Sewer Lord||130996]])"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/83/
msgid "[[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]]"
msgstr "[[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/83/
msgid "Make huge attack summons"
msgstr "做出巨大的召唤物"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/2/
msgid "Mechs - Magnetics"
msgstr ""

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/2/
msgid "Generate Magnetics with an early [[Holo Rover||115674]] or [[Scrap Scraper||98592]]. Then, reborn [[Ingenious Inventor||131606]] to stabilize. Resummon it with [[Kangor's Apprentice||59935]] and/or Titus Rivendare. Have some mech summons in the back, such as [[Auto Assembler||120025]] and reborn put on [[Deflect-o-bot||61930]] or [[Falling Sky Golem||130798]]."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/2/
msgid "Magnetic Generation ([[Scrap Scraper||98592]]) + [[Ingenious Inventor||131606]]"
msgstr ""

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/2/
msgid "Magnetic Generation ([[Scrap Scraper||98592]])"
msgstr ""

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/2/
msgid "Magnetize mechs and scale attack"
msgstr ""

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "Undead - Overflow"
msgstr "亡灵 - 挤爆"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "When the [[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]] deathrattle gets triggered, it'll buff your whole board via the [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] + [[Catacomb Crasher||114379]] combo. Use [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] to further proc Cadaver's deathrattle. Instead of [[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]], you may also use [[Lava Lurker||80747]] if you've stacked it with a lot of [[Surf n' Surf||103674]] deathrattles early. You may choose to use [[Archlich Kel'Thuzad||105518]] on a reborn Catacomb Crasher to duplicate it every turn."
msgstr "当 [[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]] 的亡语被触发时，它会通过 [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] + [[Catacomb Crasher||114379]] 的组合来强化你的整个棋盘。使用 [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] 来进一步触发遗骸看管者的亡语。如果你在早期堆叠了很多 [[Surf n' Surf||103674]] 的亡语，如果你在早期用很多 [[Surf n' Surf||103674]] 堆叠了很多亡语，你也可以用 [[Lava Lurker||80747]]。你可以选择以复生的古墓捣蛋鬼为目标使用[[Archlich Kel'Thuzad||105518]]，每回合复制它。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "Overflow unit ([[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]]) + [[Catacomb Crasher||114379]]"
msgstr "挤爆随从 ([[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]]) + [[Catacomb Crasher||114379]]"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "[[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]]\n"
"[[Lava Lurker||80747]] + [[Surf n' Surf||103674]]"
msgstr "[[Cadaver Caretaker||113158]]\n"
"[[Lava Lurker||80747]] + [[Surf n' Surf||103674]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/6/
msgid "Overflow your board to scale"
msgstr "挤掉召唤物来成长"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "Beasts - RDU"
msgstr "野兽 - 自伤"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "Use [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]] to generate lots of beasts every turn. [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]], [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]], reborn, and [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] all amplify this effect. When you have your scaling setup with [[Rabid Panther||127111]] + [[Iridescent Skyblazer||107937]] or double Rabid Panther, start buying every single beast to scale your board."
msgstr "使用 [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]] 的组合每回合生成大量野兽。[[Monstrous Macaw||62230]], [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]], 复生和 [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] 都能增强此效果。当你用 [[Rabid Panther||127111]] + [[Iridescent Skyblazer||107937]] 或双狂乱的猎豹建立起成长体系时，开始购买所有野兽来扩大你的棋盘。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "[[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]] + [[Rabid Panther||127111]]"
msgstr "[[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]] + [[Rabid Panther||127111]]"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "[[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]]\n"
"[[Rabid Panther||127111]]"
msgstr "[[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Hunting Tiger Shark||128168]]\n"
"[[Rabid Panther||127111]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/70/
msgid "Cycle beasts to damage themselves and scale"
msgstr "循环使用野兽并对它们造成伤害来强化"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/86/
msgid "Dragons - Shiny Ring"
msgstr "龙 - 闪亮的戒指"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/86/
msgid "Scale your spells using [[Felfire Conjurer||120299]] or [[Tranquil Meditative||119942]]. Then, use [[Ring Bearer||126631]] to cast as many shiny rings mid combat as possible. In order to attack as many times as possible, use [[Twilight Hatchling||126741]] and [[Twilight Broodmother||127236]] paired with [[Titus Rivendare||97408]]. Finally, [[Maelstrom Emergent||126633]] serves as a multiplier for the comp, while [[Persistent Poet||108463]] is able to capture permanent stats."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/86/
msgid "Spell scaling ([[Felfire Conjurer||120299]]) + [[Ring Bearer||126631]]"
msgstr "法术强化 ([[Felfire Conjurer||120299]]) + [[Ring Bearer||126631]]"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/86/
msgid "Spell scaling ([[Felfire Conjurer||120299]])"
msgstr "法术强化 ([[Felfire Conjurer||120299]])"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/86/
msgid "Attack many times to scale board in combat"
msgstr "在战斗中攻击多次来强化棋盘"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid "Demons - Shop Buff"
msgstr "恶魔 - 商店强化"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid "Scale your shop somehow, usually it's through [[Shadowdancer||120662]], [[Felemental||97553]], or [[Consummate Conqueror||130079]]. Then, add fodders to your shop to capture the buffed minions in shop. Typically you have an economy setup with [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + damage rewinder ([[Ashen Corruptor||121687]]) which allows you to cycle a lot of cards. Every card you cycle will add a lot of fodders to eat because of [[Twisted Wrathguard||130662]]. There's another line where you can add fodders to your shop using [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Laboratory Assistant||130075]]."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid "Buffed Shop ([[Shadowdancer||120662]]) + [[Ashen Corruptor||121687]] + [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"
msgstr "强化商店 ([[Shadowdancer||120662]]) + [[Ashen Corruptor||121687]] + [[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]\n"
"Demon midgame ([[Woodland Defiler||130076]])"
msgstr "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]]\n"
"恶魔中期过度 ([[Woodland Defiler||130076]])"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/41/
msgid "Scale and consume shop"
msgstr "强化并吞噬商店"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/81/
msgid "Elementals - Shop Buff/Spells"
msgstr "元素 - 商店强化/法术"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/81/
msgid "First, buff the shop. This is usually done by having [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]] + [[Dancing Barnstormer||99523]] or [[En-Djinn Blazer||126175]]. Keep [[Leyline Surfacer||130294]] for stats. Double the effect of the [[Arcane Absorption||130311]] you get from Leyline using [[Balinda Stonehearth||130298]]. In the endgame, scale up [[Wildfire Elemental||64189]]."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/81/
msgid "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + shop buff ([[En-Djinn Blazer||126175]] + [[Rylak Metalhead||98829]])"
msgstr "[[Brann Bronzebeard||96786]] + 商店Buff([[En-Djinn Blazer|||126175]] + [[Rylak Metalhead|||98829])"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/81/
msgid "Make big units in shop to scale."
msgstr "在商店中造出大随从来成长。"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/73/
msgid "Dragons - Spells"
msgstr "龙 - 法术"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/73/
msgid "[[Fire-Forged Evoker||120301]] scales with the amount of spells you cast. Your spell generation may come from cycling cards with [[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]] and [[Proud Privateer||122520]]. Another option for spell generation is [[Ring Bearer||126631]] + [[Twilight Broodmother||127236]], each attack casts a spell which scales your evoker mid combat. Leave [[Persistent Poet||108463]] on your board to capture permanent stats from Evoker."
msgstr ""

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/73/
msgid "[[Fire-forged Evoker||120301]] + spell generation ([[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]], [[Ring Bearer||126631]])"
msgstr "[[Fire-forged Evoker||120301]] + 法术生成 ([[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]], [[Ring Bearer||126631]])"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/73/
msgid "[[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]]\n"
"[[Fire-forged Evoker||120301]]"
msgstr "[[Sky Admiral Rogers||122516]]\n"
"[[Fire-forged Evoker||120301]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/73/
msgid "Cast spells to scale dragons"
msgstr "释放酒馆法术扩大龙的属性"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid "Beasts - Summons"
msgstr "野兽 - 召唤"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid "[[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] + [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] and [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] gives a huge aura affect to all beasts you summon. Usually, you want to taunt and reborn the Goldrinn so the Macaw always procs it and it always dies. [[Sewer Lord||130996]] is the best summon beast to run in this comp."
msgstr "[[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] + [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]] 和 [[Titus Rivendare||97408]] 会为所有你召唤的野兽提供强大的光环效果。通常你需要让戈德林获得嘲讽和复生，这样鹦鹉就能持续触发该效果，而戈德林也会不断死亡。[[Sewer Lord||130996]] 是该流派中最佳的野兽召唤选择。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid "[[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] + beast summons ([[Sewer Lord||130996]])"
msgstr "[[Goldrinn, the Great Wolf||59955]] + 野兽召唤 ([[Sewer Lord||130996]])"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid "[[Titus Rivendare||97408]] + [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]]"
msgstr "[[Titus Rivendare||97408]] + [[Monstrous Macaw||62230]]"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/12/
msgid "Scale summoned beasts in combat"
msgstr "在战斗中召唤强化的野兽"

#: name | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/8/
msgid "Murlocs - Venom Scam"
msgstr "鱼人 - 下毒"

#: how_to_play | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/8/
msgid "Buy all the scam cards and try to preserve placements by killing as many units as possible. Keep your strongest units on the board (that's why you want to concentrate stats!) and fill the rest of the board with units that may be able to trade 1 for 1. Aim to golden [[Diremuck Forager||108922]] and give it venom using [[Bile Spitter||122219]]. Then, the Diremuck will pull many scam units from your hand."
msgstr "购买所有的下毒单卡，尽可能多杀一些随从以保住排名。保留你最强战力的卡牌（所以你才需要集中精力研究统计数据！），用可以各种能1换1的随从填充空余棋盘。目标是金色的 [[Diremuck Forager||108922]] 并通过 [[Bile Spitter||122219]] 给它上毒。然后凶饿的觅食者会把你手牌中的下毒卡拉到场上。"

#: when_to_commit | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/8/
msgid "When you have no future or are clearly getting outstatted"
msgstr "当你觉得没有未来或明显快被淘汰时"

#: common_enablers | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/8/
msgid "Getting outscaled"
msgstr "快被淘汰了"

#: summary | https://hsreplay.net/battlegrounds/comps/8/
msgid "Buy scam cards and try to preserve placements"
msgstr "购买下毒卡牌，试图吃烂分"

